1. *Džoiju* treba nova lopta. (Džoi needs a new ball.)
2. Nemaš li ti *džoia*? (Don't you have your joy?)
3. Ona je veoma *džoičasta* osoba. (She is a very joyful person.)
4. Završila je svoj posao *džoijem* u koraku. (She finished her job with joy in her step.)
5. Svi su se *džoili* nakon pobede. (Everyone rejoiced after the victory.)
6. Nije mogla sakriti *džoi* u svom glasu. (She couldn't hide the joy in her voice.)
7. *Džoiov* osmeh bio je neprocenjiv. (Joy's smile was priceless.)
8. Ova pesma u meni budi *džoi*. (This song brings me joy.)
9. Deca su *džoiala* dok su se igrala. (The children were joyful while they played.)
10. Njihova veza obilovala je *džoiem*. (Their relationship was filled with joy.)